Installation
------------
If you are running out of CVS, run ./autogen.sh to create configure.

You will need to download the Samba source tree. Run:

$ cd $SAMBADIR/source
$ ./configure
$ make proto
$ cd $PDBSQLDIR
$ ./configure --with-samba-dir=$SAMBADIR
$ make
$ make install 

Run ./configure --help for a list of additional options.

Configuration
-------------
See the Samba HOWTO Collection and the other README files in this directory for 
details.
